## Onboarding a New Developer

1. Install [.NET SDK 8+](https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download)
2. Clone repository
3. Run `make build && make test` — both should pass immediately
4. Read `src/Domain/README.md` and `src/Application/README.md` for layer conventions
5. Pick an issue, create a feature branch, add a failing test, implement, open PR
